1
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,750
Delusional fantasies

2
00:01:50,330 --> 00:01:52,290
As foolish as Lin Minghua

3
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:32,370
Elder sister

4
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,950
Aren't you curious why I'm here?

5
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,500
Did you come to laugh at me?

6
00:02:40,450 --> 00:02:41,700
Or is it because of Xiao Jingyang

7
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,290
who has already decided how to deal with me?

8
00:02:45,290 --> 00:02:47,290
Third brother Gu Nian, out of brotherly affection,

9
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,580
wants to exile you,

10
00:02:49,660 --> 00:02:51,080
never to return.

11
00:02:52,450 --> 00:02:53,250
But

12
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:59,250
I'm not satisfied with that punishment.

13
00:03:09,450 --> 00:03:10,620
What do you want, then?

14
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:13,200
Lin Mingxuan killed Zhu Lan

15
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,370
all to avenge Wang Yiqiang.

16
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:20,750
But you

17
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:25,450
are also responsible for the deaths of Minghua and Father.

18
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,120
You want to kill me?

19
00:03:32,370 --> 00:03:35,290
I've gotten some poison recently.

20
00:03:35,290 --> 00:03:36,290
I wonder

21
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:41,200
how it compares to the poison you used on Third Brother.

22
00:03:42,370 --> 00:03:43,910
Which one is more potent?

23
00:03:46,410 --> 00:03:47,910
Xiao Jingyu, what are you doing?

24
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,580
Are you crazy?

25
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,250
I want to see Xiao Jingyang.

26
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:52,000
Guards!

27
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,370
I want to see Xiao Jingyang!

28
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,160
Let go of me!

29
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:56,000
Third Brother is busy taking over as city lord.

30
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,410
He doesn't have time to see you.

31
00:04:00,950 --> 00:04:02,000
Let go of me!

32
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:12,000
It hurts a lot, doesn't it?

33
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:16,000
But compared to the pain Third Brother has endured these past years,

34
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,410
compared to Minghua's death,

35
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:22,200
what you're feeling is nothing.

36
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,370
Xiao Jingyu,

37
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:26,910
you hate me so much,

38
00:04:26,910 --> 00:04:28,660
so why don't you just kill me?

39
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:29,620
Killing you

40
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,080
would be letting you off too easily.

41
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,120
It hurts so much.

42
00:04:39,330 --> 00:04:40,370
Xiao Jingyu,

43
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:42,500
you can't treat me like this.

44
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:46,660
This poison isn't fatal.

45
00:04:46,790 --> 00:04:49,040
But it will flare up once a month.

46
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:51,000
Just like what you experienced just now.

47
00:04:51,410 --> 00:04:53,450
Third Brother couldn't bring himself to kill you.

48
00:04:54,410 --> 00:04:55,660
Neither can I.

49
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:58,950
But I can make sure that for the rest of your life,

50
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:01,330
you live in constant remorse.

51
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,370
Get some rest now.

52
00:05:19,450 --> 00:05:21,000
Your wounds haven't even healed yet.

53
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,750
And you're working day and night like this.

54
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:23,450
It's nothing.

55
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:26,080
I'll only feel at ease once everything is taken care of.

56
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,750
You still have to take your medicine obediently.

57
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:31,950
Master had someone specially deliver this.

58
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,000
Alright.

59
00:05:36,290 --> 00:05:37,160
I'll do as you say.

60
00:05:48,910 --> 00:05:50,700
I'm leaving tomorrow.

61
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:52,870
Are you really not going to say goodbye to them?

62
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,370
No.

63
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,200
I might not be able to return this time.

64
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:01,580
Don't say such things.

65
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:07,580
My master is like Hua Tuo reborn.

66
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,450
He will definitely be able to save you.

67
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:12,700
Yes.

68
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,540
Master will definitely be able to save me.

69
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:17,330
I've already sent a message to Master.

70
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:20,000
I asked him to personally officiate our wedding.

71
00:06:21,660 --> 00:06:22,540
Xiao Jingyang.

72
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:27,450
This time, you must keep your word.

73
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:01,950
Third Brother dumped the troublesome job of city lord on me.

74
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,120
And now he wants to run away.

75
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:05,540
Young Lord,

76
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,540
I do not wish to become an official at court.

77
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:09,620
I only want to follow you forever.

78
00:07:09,910 --> 00:07:10,750
Young Madam,

79
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:12,450
please take me with you.

80
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:13,790
I can take care of you both.

81
00:07:13,790 --> 00:07:14,910
This time, as we leave,

82
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:16,620
we don't know when we'll return.

83
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:18,950
You are also of marriageable age now.

84
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,620
It's because I didn't want you all to be like this

85
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,620
that I chose to leave without saying goodbye.

86
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:24,910
Wu Liuqi,

87
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,620
Second Brother is about to become the city lord.

88
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,910
He needs his own people by his side.

89
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:29,790
If you are there,

90
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:30,950
I will feel more at ease.

91
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:33,040
Second Brother,

92
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,620
being city lord is a tough job.

93
00:07:36,450 --> 00:07:38,450
But with Teacher and Wu Liuqi to assist,

94
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:39,830
I can rest assured.

95
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:41,250
Third Brother,

96
00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:42,040
that's enough.

97
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:43,580
The road ahead is long and uncertain.

98
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:46,910
Until we meet again.

99
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,450
Why are you still standing there like an idiot?

100
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:07,040
From now on

101
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:09,830
you will be my wife.

102
00:10:10,830 --> 00:10:12,040
I always have been.

103
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:14,910
In every wedding of our past lives,

104
00:10:15,290 --> 00:10:16,870
I always had some concerns in my heart.

105
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,410
I never really looked closely.

106
00:10:22,370 --> 00:10:24,250
Turns out my Mingxuan is so beautiful.

107
00:10:26,830 --> 00:10:28,160
I only had one cup of wine,

108
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:29,950
how did I get drunk already?

109
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,950
At this very moment,

110
00:10:37,450 --> 00:10:39,700
I finally have you completely.
